- Tasks 1-6 are all in `shippingService.ts` — execute sequentially
- Task 7 is in `CheckoutScreen.tsx` + `ShippingMethodPicker.tsx`
- Task 8 is in `CheckoutScreen.tsx` + requires DB migration

