## Verification Plan

### Automated
1. `tsc --noEmit` — no type errors
2. Console test: `haversineDistanceKm(14.5995, 120.9842, 10.3157, 123.8854)` ≈ 565km
3. Console test: `getDistanceTier('standard', 565)` → 500-1500km tier, baseRate 180

### Manual
1. Checkout with seller that has GPS coords → distance-based fee shown
2. Checkout with seller that has NO coords and NO province → error banner "seller has not set location"
3. Checkout with international seller (country ≠ PH) → blue International Shipping card, ₱70 flat fee
4. Change address mid-checkout → fees recalculate with new distance
5. Same-day method only appears when distance < 50km
